<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.3.4">
<l>caṅkiṉ valampuriyum cēvaṭik kiṇkiṇiyu</l>
<l>maṅkaic carivaḷaiyum nāṇu maraittoṭaru</l>
<l>maṅkaṇ vicumpi lamararkaḷ pōttantār</l>
<l>ceṅkaṭ karumukilē tālēlō tēvaki ciṅkamē tālēlō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The immortals there in heaven sent a right-spiraled conch,</l>
<l>tinkling anklets for [your] red feet,</l>
<l>bangles for [your] hands, a string, and waist chain.</l>
<l>Black cloud, red-eyed [one], tālēlō! The lion of Devakī, tālēlō!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
